
we need to design apis for endusers. covering both web and mobile apps.

mobile app:
 - login screen
     - phone number is provided, onclick of login button, otp is sent to the phone number.

- otp screen
    - otp is sent to the phone number.
    - user enters the otp, and clicks on verify button.
    - if otp is verified, this phone number is checked in the database.
    - if phone number is not found, user is taken to terms and conditions screen.
    - if phone number is found, user is logged in.
    - if otp is not verified, user is asked to enter the otp again.

- terms and conditions screen
    - user is asked to accept the terms and conditions.
    - if user accepts the terms and conditions, user is redirected to member registration screen.
    - if user does not accept the terms and conditions, user cannot proceed further.

- member registration screen
    - user is asked to enter the following information:
        - upload photo [optional]
        - name
        - email
        - gender
        - date of birth
        - blood group [optional]
        - height [optional]
        - weight [optional]
    - user clicks on register button.
    - user is redirected to choosing subscription screen.

- choosing subscription screen
    - user is asked to choose the subscription plan.
    - user can choose the following subscription plans
    - user sees list of subscription plans with a default selected plan.
    - user sees list of addons
    - user can add or remove addons from the selected plan.
    - user can skip the subscription and continue with the home screen too.
    - after selecting the plan and addons, user clicks on continue button.
    - user is redirected to payment screen. [cashfree payment gateway is integrated]
    - onsuccess of payment, user is redirected to home screen.

- home screen
    - user gets his profile details.
    - user can see list of banners to be fetched through api.
    - onclick appointments, user will see list of appointments.
    - onclick of add new appointment, user will see the appointment form.
    - onclick of medical history, user will see his medical history.
    - user will be able to see his doctor, navigator, his id card details.
    - user can see ecommerce products and can add to cart.
    - user can create subprofile for his family members.
    - user can update their profile details.
    - user fetch terms and conditions from the database.
    - user can see faq from the database.
    - user can see stats from the database.
    - user should be able to upload prescriptions in image or pdf format.




Web app:
 - login screen
    - phone number is provided, onclick of login button, otp is sent to the phone number.

- otp screen
    - otp is sent to the phone number.
    - user enters the otp, and clicks on verify button.

- home screen
    - user can see list of banners to be fetched through api.
    - user can see his doctor to be fetched through api.
    - user can see his navigator to be fetched through api.
    - user can see his id card details to be fetched through api.
    - user can see list of ecommerce products to be fetched through api.
    - user can see list of faq to be fetched through api.
    - user can see stats to be fetched through api.
    - user can see list of appointments to be fetched through api.
    - user can book an appointment.
    - user can see list of medical history to be fetched through api.
    - user can see list of subprofiles to be fetched through api.
    
